Package org.persona.middleware.service.process

Class Summary
Conversion A PERSONA-specific value function for binding output parameters stating that the given output parameter represents a converted representation of a reachable property.
EffectExpression Support for constructing a special OWL-S expr:Expression (xmlns:expr="http://www.daml.org/services/owl- s/1.1/generic/Expression.owl#") that can be used to define process effects according to the PERSONA model (see ProcessEffect).
OutputBinding Support for constructing an OWL-S http://www.daml.org/services/owl-s/1.1/Process.owl#OutputBinding that can be used in the definition of process results according to the PERSONA model.
ProcessEffect Support for the PERSONA model of process effects.
